c: 3
v: 64
t: "Nabiyow keenik ixxic:kitab maraw (yahuud kee Nasaara kinnuk) Qadli Qangaray nee kee sin fanal massah tanî fanah Ama, woh Yallak-sa tu- Aqbude waynaah Agleh tu-kaat hee waynaah, Yallak kalah gari garu Yallitteh nek haysite waam kinni, tokkel usun Yalla inkittoysaanam cineeniih Ama meqe Seecot derre caben ken tekkek, toysa isin kitab maraw nanu muslimiiniy Yalla inkittossa kinninoomuh neh Sumaaqita keenik ixxica moominiiney"